   this.preOrder = preOrder;
   this.inOrder = inOrder;
   this.postOrder = postOrder;
}
```
后序遍历的打印顺序

![](2838289-40ce1a6b62a8dfc2.png)

按上图的输出顺序是：` 2 -> 8 -> 9 -> 9 -> 4 -> 3 -> 13 -> 21 -> 18  -> 10 `

![](2838289-b98b04bb61c0aa6c.png)

